      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Gandy",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Reference is made to my memorandum of September 23,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "1957, on the captioned matter which reflected an Intelligence",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Advisory Committee (IAC) evaluation of an Air Defense",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Command (ADC) report that radar stations at Montauk Point,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Long Island, New York, and Benton, Pennsylvania, detected an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "unidentified object proceeding in a westward direction with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "an altitude of 50,000 feet and a speed of 2,000 knots",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "(approximately 2,300 miles per hour) on September 20, 1957.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "The IAC intelligence evaluation of this report reflected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "that \"It is highly improbable that a Soviet operation is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "responsible for the unidentified flying object reports of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "September 20, 1957.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Today, at an Executive Session of the IAC,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "General Millard Lewis, Director, Air Force Intelligence,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "advised that although the ADC has not completed its investigation",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "of the evidence on this matter, there are continuing",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "indications that the object detected was an atmospheric",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "phenomenon. The radar pickups now reflect speed variations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "in the object's course, ranging from 1,500 miles per hour to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "4,500 miles per hour. This latter speed is improbable",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "according to U. S. scientific theory for any type flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "object which this could conceivably be. General Lewis added",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "that the present sun spots are associated with the peculiar",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "radar activity throughout the globe and that this could have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "some cause for the captioned report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "ACTION:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "Liaison will report further information on this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "matter as quickly as it is developed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "status": "blank"
